#. module: no_pdf_preview_print
#: model:ir.module.module,description:no_pdf_preview_print.module_meta_information
msgid ""
"PDF Preview Before Print intercepts the print/download action and shows a "
"clean full-screen preview before the document is printed or downloaded. "
"Keyboard shortcuts (P/D/Esc), single and batch reports, zero configuration."
msgstr ""
"打印前PDF预览会拦截打印/下载操作，"
"在文档实际打印或下载之前显示"
"一个整洁的全屏预览。支持键盘"
"快捷键（P/D/Esc）、单条记录和批量"
"报告，无需任何配置。"

